{"desc": "This locket was dredged from the remains of a long-dead sea monster. The amulet has 3 charges. While wearing this strange oyster-shaped pendant, you can use an action to expend a charge and choose one creature within 30 feet that is laughing, singing, or speaking. The target makes a DC 15 Wisdom _saving throw_  or you steal its voice. As long as you are wearing the amulet, you can speak with the target’s voice. For as long as you possess a target’s voice in the amulet, the target is unable to speak. 

