The spirit-trapping camera has 3 charges and regains 1 each dawn. When the last charge is expended, roll a d20\. On a 1, it becomes a mundane photochemical camera.", "document__slug": "a5e", "document__title": "Level Up Advanced 5e", "document__url": "https://a5esrd.com/a5esrd", "name": "Spirit-Trapping Camera", "rarity": "Very Rare", "requires_attunement": "", "slug": "spirit-trapping-camera-a5e", "type": "Wondrous Item"}

